Text.string: Hey! C'mere. Circle up.||—I said gather 'ROUND!
RING THE BELL!
Ring the doorbell, Vault Hunter!
Come onnn. Just, ring the... ring the dingaling. Ring—ringaling the dingaling.
Just ring the bell. Just ring it!
Get lost, Vault Thieves. I ain't in the sacrificin' mood—and take your stupid hearts with you!
Hand over the skag, or I kick in your teeth.||—Ah, y'know what, came in a little hot there. Just give me the skag.
You trespass upon the sacred bond of friendship betwixt a girl and her beast!
Dude, just give us Tina's skag and we'll leave you alone.
Tina said you're feeling sad. You sad? Need to... talk about it?
Man, I KNEW something was bumming her out! Must be all this culty crap. Okay—cover it all up with my happy li'l hearts so Sheega quits being such a crazy-pants, okay?
[singing] Makin' it all pretty. Makin' it all pretty. Dis a pretty ditty 'cause Sheega been a shitty bitty!
All right, sacrifice it is. Sic 'em, hounds!
Sheega? Just gimme back my Enrique-sweety-buns and I'll call off the ruthless exterior decorator! Okay?
Every skag you've ever owned is DEAD! Enrique's better off with me!
Float like a varkid, sting like a... a-also like a varkid.
PUNCH THE HEART ALREADY!
Punch iiiit.
Give it a classic whackity-whack.
Y'all... might wanna stand back.
Ka-BOOM! Now get in there and find my fluffy little joy-muffin, Enrico Suave!
Oh my gawwwwwd! My sweet teeny-tiny! Isn't he just the cutest?! I love his li'l face. Yo, go—go grab—go grab some skaggy treats for my widdle guy, okay?
We won't let Sheega hurt you anymore. I promise.
Come to me, little hound. We are here to break your chains.
I know I'm, like, covered in skag blood. But I'm not gonna hurt you, little one!
Come here, sweet boy. I won't bite if you don't.
Bad boy, Enrique.
Excuse me?! He is NOT a bad boy! He's the best boy! The best-est!
She hurt my 'Rique. All right, that's it! You know what to do.
Oh, you wanna feed skags, huh? I can arrange that.
You're okay now, Enrique! Come on home to mama! Come to mama!
Enrique! Awww, come here, my ugly little lovey dove! Yes, my sweetest-est man-friend! Who's the best doggy?! Who's the best doggy?! ANSWER ME! WHO'S THE BEST DOGGY?!
Now leave me to my snuggles! [giggle]
Who's the cutie-est skaggy butthead? Is it you? Is it you? Yes! It is you, Enrique, my snuggle-mush tiny-paws. I missed you so much!

Are you the tiniest?! How'd you get so tiny? Look at that little face. Where'd you get a face like that, huh? Did you cut it off a cuter skag and steal the cute? Did you steal the cute out of his very SOUL?! Huh? Huh?!
Did you eat all the cutie-pies until you turned into the cutie-est of cutie-pies? Oh, I bet you did! I bet you did, ya li'l fatty!

Oh, you're so sweet! I'm gonna eat you up! That's right! I'm gonna start with your widdle toes, and I'm gonna season 'em with a very tasteful balsalmic glaze, and I'm gonna put you in a little oven, and I'm gonna roast you at 350 degrees, and then I'm gonna gobble you up!
Man, that got weird. Why do I always wanna eat cute stuff? Should I get that checked out? Anyway, what about just a nibble? Just a widdle nibble? Chomp chomp chomp chomp chomp, I'm gonna get you!
Awright, you ready for this, girl?

Okay, so, I needed someone to watch my fuzzy-shanks li'l hottie-boy, Enrique IV. And I THOUGHT I could trust my besty pet skag with my sexy-exy, Sheega. But now she won't give him back! But it's okay. I think she's just havin' some, y'know, some sad times right now. Because, y'know. I broke up with her ass. BUT, now, she's holdin' my Enrique like a cuddle-hostage! So here. Take these happy li'l heart decorations, and, uh, we're gonna go get my skag back.

See, Enrique Two... he got eated by a bigger skag, which... oof, sucked. And then, Enrique the Three died at the farmer's market... don't wanna talk about that, but, y'know, safe to say I can't go back to the farmer's market anymore.
Now go ahead and ring the bell and let's see if these hearts made Sheega happy again.
Hey. It's cool. You know Tina always got a plan B. A plan BOMB, baby!||First, go punch that heart. Then go punch SHEEGA IN THE HEART!
Okay, great. Now get you over to Casa de Sheega—and then we're gonna brighten her day.

An' if Sheega hurts one sweet little scale on that sweet little boy's sweet little skag butt, I'm gonna rip her face, and then I'll put her face down her own throat, and I'm gonna take that, I'm gonna put it in a bomb, and I'll send it to SPACE!
Bad, bad boy!
GOOD RIDDANCE, YOU SHITBIRD!
These are dark days, tomodachi. When friends turns on friends, and tricksy ladies turn skagsnapper.||Anyway, here's your reward!
Oooh-hoh-hoh-oh, she did—she did not just—oookay! We were TRYIN' to do this the nice way, but now dis bitch gon' get it.||She's... gon'... get it!
That's one of Sheega's evil skags. KILL IT!
Those skags bad to the skelly. Evil runs deep.
My Enrique is the only good skag in the whole world 'cause I raised him RIGHT—and that ain't him.
Hounds! Attack!
More hounds!
Sic 'em, hounds!
Release the hounds!
Vaulty-Vault, let Enrique out the back gate, please.
Metaphorically, though. Not—not, not, not like, with a bomb. Tryin' to solve this one with smiles for a change. Character growth, biiitch!
Yo. For reals, though? I—I gots to get my Enrique back. I'd kill the whole world for that sweet li'l monster boy. And I promised myself I would not lose another... [sniffle] Don't cry, Tina!
WHAT?! What's all this culty crappity-crap?||[gasp] Sheega went and nested down with those crazy-pants Calypsos?! She's a damn COV now?! Hohhhh, no-no-no-no-no no no NO.
